snippet: The teenager Lexi Thompson is five shots behind the leaders Yani Tseng and Karin Sjodin at the Kraft Nabisco Championship, the year’s first major L.P.G.A. tournament.
abstract: Golf Roundup; teenager Lexi Thompson is five shots behind the leaders Yani Tseng and Karin Sjodin after the third round at the Kraft Nabisco Championship, the year’s first major LPGA tournament; other golf results noted.

byline.original: By KAREN CROUSE and THE ASSOCIATED PRESS

lead_paragraph: The teenager Lexi Thompson is five shots behind the leaders Yani Tseng and Karin Sjodin at the Kraft Nabisco Championship, the year’s first major L.P.G.A. tournament.

headline.seo: Thompson Trails Sjodin and Tseng at Kraft Nabisco
headline.main: Thompson Seeks Major Title and a Prom Date
